{"tid":1037751,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"埋離睇~~~我認我係膚淺...","createTime":"2019-02-26T07:11:37.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-26T10:29:43.000Z","uid":56874,"like":0,"dislike":17,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"c3f945f10bce7b943f46b7385716cf64864ca1ca","tid":1037751,"uid":56874,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-26T07:11:37.000Z","msg":"識左一個女仔，同佢相處左都一段時間啦<br />\n大家一齊出街玩過好多次<br />\n溜冰，游水，打機之類好多都岩玩大家<br />\n發覺大家興趣好夾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n真係好難遇到一個80%興趣都相同ge女仔，唔係only掛住行街買衫<br />\n佢樣貌係10分我諗係7分<br />\n但我唔係話佢樣唔靚，但個樣就係唔係我鐘意果個(類型)<br />\n其實出離玩嘅時候佢已經會主動有身體接觸我，我都對佢有feel，但就係次次都未有最大衝動和feel去拖實佢或者錫落去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n好多人都話搵同一個有共同興趣嘅伴侶係好重要，我都知，但自己個心話比自己聽，唔係鐘意嘅類型所以未有最大feeling令自己錫落去...<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n好怕再咁拖落去唔比名份佢，會慢慢失去佢<br />\n唔同佢開始住都係因為想諗清楚，唔想一陣拍得短時間傷害了她<br />\n各位絲巴打有冇咩意見可以比到我<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f06ab0b0e1dd4a9c83a393914909eb23bfc96871","tid":1037751,"uid":56874,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-26T07:16:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a800d389ee74672c7c69ac580a578787a2b1caff","tid":1037751,"uid":122134,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-26T07:17:49.000Z","msg":"共同興趣真係緊要<br />\n係等於話題<br />\n你揀個樣靚 無計傾既<br />\n到時佢都係比人溝走"},{"pid":"4fe74f0ff267ca05a6e7d4f4c144dd0fcbd54c38","tid":1037751,"uid":56874,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a800d389ee74672c7c69ac580a578787a2b1caff","tid":1037751,"uid":122134,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-26T07:17:49.000Z","msg":"共同興趣真係緊要<br />\n係等於話題<br />\n你揀個樣靚 無計傾既<br />\n到時佢都係比人溝走"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-26T07:30:05.000Z","msg":"佢個樣唔係差呀，中上樣<br />\n我唔係要㨂明星級咁嘅靚女呀<br />\n係我要鐘意果隻類型，佢有60-70%似係我鐘意果個類型<br />\n如果係我鐘意果個類型，肥肥地我都會有衝動<br />\n次次同佢出街都玩到好有feel，但當佢主動同我身體接觸，我又衝唔同去拖住佢或者錫佢...<br />\n佢同我真係好夾，我同佢好開心玩到，但真係唔知點解去唔到最後一下<br />\n我個心依家都好痛苦<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d9ae5be4ed1f476f9c6482944fc34f26737f4d33","tid":1037751,"uid":56874,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-26T07:32:52.000Z","msg":"有冇人可以幫下我<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e7b1416f2dda40ab1e96e552783d3f488402b52e","tid":1037751,"uid":155818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-26T07:33:44.000Z","msg":"啱FEEL就直接拖佢去酒店啦"},{"pid":"93d2c9aeb60d0ebc5f594ee7898b03e35ed8de95","tid":1037751,"uid":56874,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e7b1416f2dda40ab1e96e552783d3f488402b52e","tid":1037751,"uid":155818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-26T07:33:44.000Z","msg":"啱FEEL就直接拖佢去酒店啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-26T07:36:12.000Z","msg":"今次認真嫁，因我玩夠啦如果妳睇返我以前果啲post...<br />\n比著我以前拖左錫左啦...<br />\n但今次我想長久和不想傷害她<br />\n所以想問清楚自己個心諗緊咩先...<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fc086d3068b72d49277bbf8849968d8ed397a2f9","tid":1037751,"uid":56874,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-26T07:40:59.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d27fbe9859e65045b6de929e073d35b2e5759158","tid":1037751,"uid":56874,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-26T07:46:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/19.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"20236c368f2269fd5bebb1ed3575b81d03a5f53b","tid":1037751,"uid":206306,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-26T07:47:38.000Z","msg":"咁你幾時先諗清楚? 定係比緊藉口自己?<br />\n<br />\n其實我覺得大家都有feel係唔洗表白都會一齊到既 只係遲早既事 會唔會個女仔都好似你咁 想諗清楚先?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a07f2553beadb6abc5d7a1b4f54bd4f2baa12059","tid":1037751,"uid":180065,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-26T07:49:43.